{"tid":1225070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔係chinese﹐唔好再I am Chinese.","createTime":"2019-06-15T06:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:40.000Z","uid":41116,"like":65,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f41b51af8f68abfccc8e97b3dc2f01a0f50c9c","tid":1225070,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"香港人唔係chinese<br />\n唔好再I am Chinese. <br />\n或者比人叫Chinese又唔糾正人<br />\n人地用粵語問 香港人會答我係香港人<br />\n用支那話問 會答我是香港人<br />\n點解一英文就答就 I am Chinese?<br />\n唔好厄自己話你個chinese係華人咁解<br />\n記住香港人係 Hong Kongese<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oP4QVth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoP4QVth.jpg&h=32296831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nI am Hong Kongese!<br />\n唔好再比人統戰<br />\n自己嘅身份認同係要由自己開始建立<br />\n外人先會意識有呢個族群"},{"pid":"e90446e0d7ca1f793a977fd88cc3f695fdaf2f67","tid":1225070,"uid":60155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9b854280feba7a3dc78265b3ea33aa8e2402fdb","tid":1225070,"uid":183567,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過咗火 集中力量集合所有人嘅力量(好多人都認同中國人身份但反條例)搞掂條例先啦 增加本土認同係靠實事 唔係靠講 6 12 就係最好例子"},{"pid":"664343110be04288e8d28251e5f1325115d2d35d","tid":1225070,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e9b854280feba7a3dc78265b3ea33aa8e2402fdb","tid":1225070,"uid":183567,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過咗火 集中力量集合所有人嘅力量(好多人都認同中國人身份但反條例)搞掂條例先啦 增加本土認同係靠實事 唔係靠講 6 12 就係最好例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n你覺得自己係chinese就繼續<br />\n我無阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef5817217a754ee98a4da88ae36c15c55b6cf11","tid":1225070,"uid":255979,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"I am HongKonger 暫時嚟講中立啲"},{"pid":"b43d66d35d3e1157f4bc43806ce4d2a00c550557","tid":1225070,"uid":50301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"八方終於可以高呼「I am Hong Kongese（我係香港人）」。英國牛津大學出版社嘅《牛津字典》網上版公佈3月份詞彙最新修訂，新加入「Hong Kongese」及「Hongkonger」，同樣解作「香港人」。有網民狂喜話「正名」係對香港人身份認同；喺英國留學嘅陶傑亦認為，出版社認同香港人係「特別嘅華人」，先會特意收錄。<br />\n陶傑話「ese」字尾一般指一個民族，例如Japanese係日裔人、Chinese指華人；「er」字尾就指一個城巿嘅人，例如New Yorker係紐約客、Londoner係倫敦人，佢就鍾意Hongkonger多啲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中間冇space<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb9f321d9dcbbc8ff762a4c2fde9d027e3a6150","tid":1225070,"uid":77685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哦"},{"pid":"9b91c255c76c8028041ebf38df722c052c21bb60","tid":1225070,"uid":88269,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f11b1969b4bc6b722e64e5bfef6fb191485f82ac","tid":1225070,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"aye"},{"pid":"d5fb5f2701adad81e675c69724eddbfe6bcc9a22","tid":1225070,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c185a5d0118eeac854323147968411d82b70dfeb","tid":1225070,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4757066e9a5487af381207dde3497a31d31e4c9d","tid":1225070,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"我係中國人啊屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡情地負皮我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}